Process ID: 74830 - AU/CYCLOHEXANE UNIT



The AU/Cyclohexane Process has three units: UDEX, Cyclohexane and AU/Cyclohexane Offsites. The UDEX is an aromatics separations unit which is now out of service. The Cyclohexane Unit manufactures cyclohexane. The AU/Cyclohexane Offsites includes storage, cooling tower, and flare. The risk management program's elements for the units listed apply to all units except as follows: Only the Cyclohexane unit has a quench system; the dikes apply only to storage tanks in the AU/Cyclohexane Unit. The emergency power and air, automatic shutoffs and purge system do not apply to the AU/Cyclohexane Offsites Unit. The flammable mixture mass noted below includes inventories of non RMP flammable chemicals and RMP flammable chemicals below the threshold quantity in the process. RMP chemicals below the threshold quantity included in the flammable mixture are: Ethane; Methane; Pentane, and Hydrogen.



