11. Incident Investigation ? Incidents are investigated using one of several industry recognized methodologies, such as Tap Root and Cause mapping, to determine system level root causes that can be remedied to prevent a reoccurrence. Employees and contractors involved in the incident are included on the investigation team. PAS-08 Incident Investigation includes a description of how the Incident Investigation element is implemented 

